external_knowledge:
- 'Instruments' refers to devices;
- 'Marred by failure' indicates the simulation status is 'failed';
- 'Journey across the realms of diodes and transistors' means the device type is either diode or transistor;
- 'Highest peaks these instruments have scaled in their parameter values' refers to the maximum parameter values recorded;
- 'Fate of these journeys' signifies the simulation status;
- 'Explorers who charted their courses' refers to the user names;
- 'Voyages that braved more than 15 parameter trials' means the simulation involves more than 15 parameter values.
